stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PENDING : ARI APPROVED

    PENDING --> VERIFIED : All 38 rules pass
    PENDING --> REJECTED : Non-critical rule fails
    PENDING --> DELAYED : Bar not confirmed or broker unavailable
    PENDING --> EMERGENCY_BLOCK : Critical safety condition

    VERIFIED --> [*] : Webhook transmitted

    REJECTED --> PENDING : New signal on next bar
    DELAYED --> PENDING : Next bar close — re-evaluate
    EMERGENCY_BLOCK --> PENDING : Manual reset only

    note right of VERIFIED
        Webhook transmitted
        Observatory: TVL_VERIFIED
    end note

    note right of REJECTED
        Webhook suppressed
        Observatory: TVL_REJECTED
        Rejection codes logged
    end note

    note right of DELAYED
        Webhook suppressed
        Observatory: TVL_DELAYED
        Signal remains valid
        Retry on next bar
    end note

    note right of EMERGENCY_BLOCK
        ALL trading halted
        Observatory: EMERGENCY_BLOCK
        Requires manual reset
    end note
